<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-372] Unmatched right parentheses truncates query</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-372</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;The query processor truncates a query when right parentheses are unmatched.&lt;br/&gt;
E.g.:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; secret AND illegal) AND access:confidential&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will not result in a ParseException instead will run as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; secret AND illegal&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Operating System: Linux&lt;br/&gt;
Platform: PC&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
